CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 23, 1951, pg. 32 reads: "More Teachers And Attendant To Senior Queen - ...Center photo: V. Elaine Hall was awarded her diploma from the college. She was an attendant to the Senior Queen last week...All are from Pitt."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of University of Pittsburgh graduate Virginia Elaine Hall, holding diploma, posed in front of Syria Mosque, Oakland
